20 C. The following provisions shall apply:
21 1. A manufacturing concern shall be entitled to the exemption
22 herein provided for each new manufacturing facility constructed,
23 each existing manufacturing facility acquired and the expansion of
24 existing manufacturing facilities on the same site, as such terms
Req. No. 17521 Page 8

1 are defined by Section 6B of Article X of the Oklahoma Constitution
